Class MidList

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--javaxipc30.MidList
public final class MidList
extends java.lang.Object

A MidList represents a list of MemSys memory segment Sections. The methods of this class are alternatives, with a more object oriented flavor, to the Xipc.MemListBuild() and Xipc.MemListAdd() methods.

See Also:
Xipc.MemListBuild(javaxipc30.Section), Xipc.MemListAdd(javaxipc30.MidList, javaxipc30.Section)

public final MidList MemListAdd(Section Section)
Adds a Section to a MidList.

Adds a Section object, representing a section of a MemSys memory segment, to a MidList.

Parameters:
Section - A Section object.
Returns:
The updated MidList object, or null if the MidList was full.
